channel.title: Sqlmap problem with dba
channel.description:
Hello fellas, today i decide to do some scans in one school site the function i used is `sqlmap -u "url" -o -b --current-user --is-dba --no-cast` everything worked smoothly then i just got `current user is DBA : False` i though its from the site, then i just randomly decide to run on 4-5 more with the same options and i got always same result? Am i doing something wrong or ? =) Thanks in advance.
Kind Regards, spylegion
